div.p: Hi there! I'm Andy, a lifelong learner with a penchant for crazy projects. I'm a freshman at Stanford University, incoming software engineering intern at Replit, president of Stanford Student Robotics, and officer on Stanford Moonshot. Previously, I was a software engineering intern on Cloudflare Magic Transit and a student researcher at the UIUC Chung Lab.
